 Taiwan Stock, S&P 500, and NASDAQ datasets exhibit\nremarkable recommendation performance of our FinGAT, comparing to\nstate-of-the-art methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Jun 2021 14:51:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-21"}
